# Tevive Wiki

Welcome to the official Tevive Wiki.

Tevive is a platform dedicated to preserving, discovering, and reviving classic games. Our mission is to keep great games alive and accessible for current and future generations.

---

## What is Tevive?

Tevive helps players rediscover classic games through a modern platform. We focus on game preservation, accessibility, and community-driven growth.

